responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "236AA6F84B0805A1F526A49F98A49D5A", "It is said that he friended the benevolent King Gallus and together they purged the land of demonic plagues. Alas, after taking human form, the evil of the light bearers destroyed the first of faith, turning him to ashes. Then the light bearers gathered his ashes only to divide them and hide ashes within a vault of ashes, Gravepeak! ")
